SCTX:
Begin dandrasScript

short deathbed
float dandrasHealth

if ( deathbed == -1 )
	return
endif

set dandrasHealth to GetHealth

if ( dandrasHealth <= 50 )
	if ( dandrasHealth < 1 )
		resurrect
		modHealth 100
	endif
	set deathbed to 1
endif

if ( deathbed == 1 )
	ForceGreeting
endif



End dandrasScript
